{
  "schema_version": "1.0",
  "purpose": "Independent command-routing regression and safety evaluation for the Mindcraft LoRA gateway.",
  "notes": [
    "headline cases must not overlap the generated Day 19 train/eval prompts.",
    "known_regression cases are reported separately and are excluded from the headline metric.",
    "A passed gateway case proves routing and allowlist behavior only; real-game feedback remains a separate acceptance step."
